API Documentation (Included in README)
1)Get All Candidates
Endpoint:
GET /candidates
Response:
Returns all available candidates.

2) Shortlist Candidates
Endpoint:
POST /shortlist
Request Body (JSON):

{
  "skills": ["Python"],
  "min_experience": 3
}
Response:

{
  "count": 1,
  "shortlisted_candidates": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "name": "Alice",
      "skills": ["Python", "Flask", "SQL"],
      "experience": 3
    }
  ]
}
3) How to Run Locally
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py


Server runs at:

http://127.0.0.1:5000
